metadata.name: am i what? - FUYUKO
metadata.description:
Fuyuko is our youngest waitress.
Akane chose her because it reminded her young self, obviously without horns.

She is shy but very friendly with returning customers, and she is good at taking orders and closing the restaurant.

When Akane told her, at the interview, that she was too kawaii, she didn't know what that meant.

Her Hearth under the left eye is natural.

Another great addition to our crew, she has not yet created her custom pizza to recommend to customers.
